      "description": "2019 sedan in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable wear including several scratches and minor dents, with some surface rust in a few areas. The interior has moderate wear \u2014 upholstery shows visible use, some trim pieces are scuffed or worn, but the overall structure is intact. Mechanically the car runs, though it has some issues that may need attention. A functional vehicle that reflects its age and use.",
